name: Drunks and Dragons - Dungeons and Dragons 5e Actual Play
Tabletop Champions - Real Play D&D 5E (DND 5e)
description: A real play Dungeons & Dragons 5th edition podcast set in the mythical lands of Irulan. We have been playing 5th edition since the early play test and new listeners may want to jump on at Episode 50 which is the beginning of a brand new Season 2 arc or at Episode 98 which is the beginning of our Season 3 arc.

name: Sneak Attack!: A Dungeons and Dragons Adventure
description: Sneak Attack! is an original Dungeons and Dragons adventure set in the world of Brannis. The game is Fifth Edition, and releases episodes every Friday.

name: Brute Force
description: Brute Force is a real-play comedic RPG podcast blended with in-character narration. We play a campaign of FATE Core (we started with World of Darkness) set in the high fantasy world of Eorith. The adventurers are a party of monsters tasked with saving a world that barely tolerates their existence.
